NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
D.C., Defendant,
and
D.W., Defendant-Petitioner. In the Matter of D.W., Jr., and B.W., Minors-Respondents. C-76 September Term 2018
080913 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 24, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-2526/2527-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
